156 /*========== Extern Function Implementations ================================*/
157 extern void FTSK_InitializeUserCodeEngine(void) {
158  /* Warning: Do not change the content of this function */
159  /* See function definition doxygen comment for details */
160  STD_RETURN_TYPE_e retval = DATA_Initialize();
161 
162  if (retval == E_NOT_OK) {
163  /* Fatal error! */
164  FAS_ASSERT(FAS_TRAP);
165  }
166 
167  /* Suspend AFE task if unused, otherwise it will preempt all lower priority tasks */
168 #if (FOXBMS_AFE_DRIVER_TYPE_FSM == 1)
169  vTaskSuspend(ftsk_taskHandleAfe);
170 #endif
171 
172  /* Init FRAM */
173  FRAM_Initialize();
174 
175  retval = SYSM_Init();
176 
177  if (retval == E_NOT_OK) {
178  /* Fatal error! */
179  FAS_ASSERT(FAS_TRAP);
180  }
181 
182  /* Warning: Do not change the content of this function */
183  /* See function definition doxygen comment for details */
184 }
185 
186 extern void FTSK_RunUserCodeEngine(void) {
187  /* Warning: Do not change the content of this function */
188  /* See function definition doxygen comment for details */
189  DATA_Task(); /* Call database manager */
190  SYSM_CheckNotifications(); /* Check notifications from tasks */
191  /* Warning: Do not change the content of this function */
192  /* See function definition doxygen comment for details */
193 }
194 
195 extern void FTSK_InitializeUserCodePreCyclicTasks(void) {
196  /* user code */
197  SYS_RETURN_TYPE_e sys_retVal = SYS_ILLEGAL_REQUEST;
198 
199  /* Init Sys */
200  sys_retVal = SYS_SetStateRequest(SYS_STATE_INITIALIZATION_REQUEST);
201 
202  /* Init port expander */
203  PEX_Initialize();
204 
205  /* Set 3rd PE pin to activate temperature/humidity sensor */
206  PEX_SetPinDirectionOutput(PEX_PORT_EXPANDER3, PEX_PIN00);
207  PEX_SetPin(PEX_PORT_EXPANDER3, PEX_PIN00);
208 
209  CONT_Initialize();
210  SPS_Initialize();
211  (void)MEAS_Initialize(); /* cast to void as the return value is unused */
212 
213  /* Initialize redundancy module */
214  (void)MRC_Initialize();
215 
216  /* This function operates under the assumption that it is called when
217  * the operating system is not yet running.
218  * In this state the return value of #SYS_SetStateRequest should
219  * always be #SYS_OK. Therefore we trap otherwise.
220  */
221  FAS_ASSERT(sys_retVal == SYS_OK);
222 
223  /* System started correctly -> Start toggling of debug LED */
224  LED_SetToggleTime(LED_NORMAL_OPERATION_ON_OFF_TIME_ms);
225 }
226 
227 extern void FTSK_RunUserCodeCyclic1ms(void) {
228  /* Increment of operating system timer */
229  /* This must not be changed, add user code only below */
230  OS_IncrementTimer();
231  DIAG_UpdateFlags();
232  /* user code */
233 #if (FOXBMS_AFE_DRIVER_TYPE_FSM == 1)
234  MEAS_Control();
235 #endif
236  CAN_ReadRxBuffer();
237 }
238 
239 extern void FTSK_RunUserCodeCyclic10ms(void) {
240  static uint8_t ftsk_cyclic10msCounter = 0;
241  /* user code */
242  SYSM_UpdateFramData();
243  SYS_Trigger(&sys_state);
244  ILCK_Trigger();
245  ADC_Control();
246  SPS_Ctrl();
247  CAN_MainFunction();
248  SOF_Calculation();
249  ALGO_MonitorExecutionTime();
250  SBC_Trigger(&sbc_stateMcuSupervisor);
251 
252  if (ftsk_cyclic10msCounter == TASK_10MS_COUNTER_FOR_50MS) {
253  MRC_ValidateAfeMeasurement();
254  MRC_ValidatePackMeasurement();
255  ftsk_cyclic10msCounter = 0;
256  }
257  /* Call BMS_Trigger function at the end of the 10ms task to allow previously
258  * called modules in this task to update respectively evaluate their new.
259  * This minimizes the delay between data evaluation and the reaction from
260  * the BMS module */
261  BMS_Trigger();
262  ftsk_cyclic10msCounter++;
263 }
264 
265 extern void FTSK_RunUserCodeCyclic100ms(void) {
266  /* user code */
267  static uint8_t ftsk_cyclic100msCounter = 0;
268 
269  /** Perform SOC and SOE calculations only every 1s. Not suited if analog
270  * integration of current sensor is NOT used. Manual integration of current
271  * requires a higher frequency.
272  */
273  if (ftsk_cyclic100msCounter == TASK_100MS_COUNTER_FOR_1S) {
274  SE_RunStateEstimations();
275  ftsk_cyclic100msCounter = 0;
276  }
277 
278  BAL_Trigger();
279  IMD_Trigger();
280  LED_Trigger();
281 
282  ftsk_cyclic100msCounter++;
283 }
284 
285 extern void FTSK_RunUserCodeCyclicAlgorithm100ms(void) {
286  /* user code */
287  static uint8_t ftsk_cyclicAlgorithm100msCounter = 0;
288 
289  ALGO_MainFunction();
290 
291  ftsk_cyclicAlgorithm100msCounter++;
292 }
293 
294 void FTSK_RunUserCodeI2c(void) {
295  /* user code */
296  PEX_Trigger();
297  HTSEN_Trigger();
298  RTC_Trigger();
299  uint32_t current_time = OS_GetTickCount();
300  OS_DelayTaskUntil(&current_time, 2u);
301 }
302 
303 void FTSK_RunUserCodeAfe(void) {
304  /* user code */
305 #if (FOXBMS_AFE_DRIVER_TYPE_NO_FSM == 1)
306  MEAS_Control();
307 #endif
308 }

312 }
